00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:45.790
That sounds like a good idea. Yeah, I think this will be great. We'll all get a chance into our research

00:01:46.189 --> 00:01:52.120
I asked Daniel to research Christian principles on neutrality

00:01:55.189 --> 00:02:03.510
Collette and Elizabeth would find examples of ones who prove loyal under pressure and for me

