My job was to call Elizabeth's new school to find out if they saluted the flag or sang the anthem

00:02:11.580 --> 00:02:15.060
Hello, hi, Mr. Johnson. Let's just Curtis Elizabeth dad

00:02:15.580 --> 00:02:22.669
We'd studied this topic when the kids were younger, but we needed reminders for these new challenges

00:02:23.669 --> 00:02:26.229
The kids found some great information

00:02:28.349 --> 00:02:30.349
Several Bible principles applied

00:02:30.870 --> 00:02:35.590
But what Jesus said at Matthew 410 was an essential foundation

00:02:37.189 --> 00:02:43.590
It is Jehovah your God you must worship and it is to him alone. You must render sacred service

00:02:44.349 --> 00:02:47.509
If we participate in a nationalistic ceremony

00:02:48.189 --> 00:02:53.030
We're sharing in worship of something or someone other than Jehovah God

00:02:53.990 --> 00:02:56.669
But what would help us know what to do?

00:02:58.189 --> 00:03:05.469
Elizabeth found some good examples to imitate the account of Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego was one of our favorites

00:03:06.189 --> 00:03:13.310
When King Nebuchadnezzar ordered them to worship the gold image they bravely stood while others bowed down

00:03:14.310 --> 00:03:20.830
They were determined to worship only Jehovah and he rescued them from the furnace and

00:03:21.949 --> 00:03:25.349
There are modern-day examples of courage like the three Hebrews

00:03:25.949 --> 00:03:36.469
Some children have had to take a stand when governments tried to force them to take part in patriotic events during wartime when feelings of national pride ran strong

00:03:37.469 --> 00:03:43.189
And despite legal victories in some countries young ones today are still put to the test

00:03:44.789 --> 00:03:47.590
We learned there was no one answer on what to do

00:03:48.870 --> 00:03:54.909
Situations are different depending on where we live or what a person does to show he's participating

00:03:56.189 --> 00:04:02.270
But in every case Christians in some way make it evident that they are respectful observers

00:04:02.909 --> 00:04:04.909
Not participants

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:11.789
We felt good because we had decided what we would do to be respectful but neutral and

00:04:12.270 --> 00:04:15.990
Showed Jehovah that our family worships him alone
